{
  "stem": "2230.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We could not, or would not, go and play with the other boys because they would just beat the things out of you and-- so we just decided not to go and play with them.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't come here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't go there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Many a times.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that's why--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that's why I joined [NON-ENGLISH] so that when-- I don't remember how long it was, how it was before the war.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, how many years.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I must have been a baby.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, a little boy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When-- when we went out, there were a bunch of us who would never go alone.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like, even to walk down the street from one corner to the other, we would go as a bunch.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You had to.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You had to.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you couldn't fight because, if you fought, the cops would come and take you away and-- and beat you up, this Albert.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had only--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jewish kids they would take away and beat them up?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was only one policeman and he was the worst there ever was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we learned, but we couldn't.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We couldn't fight back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To whom?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What they said when I told them I was beaten up?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They never said fight back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They just said, next time, run.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Run.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Don't get into a fight.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But that was not only me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a way of life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know you're going to go out, you're going to go for a walk, you're going to get hit, you're going to get kicked, you're going to be spat on, and you're going to be called Zyd.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I guess maybe it was an identification that I was a Zyd.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I believed that I was a Zyd.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
